Description: pdbreak
        =======
        
        A quick break to your python script.
        
        Usage
        -----
        
        .. code:: py
        
            #!/usr/bin/env python
            # encoding: utf-8
            print 1
            import pdbreak # import pdb;pdb.set_trace()
            print 2
        
        Run your script
        
        .. code:: sh
        
            $ python test.py
            1
            --Return--
            (Pdb) n
            > /home/lyc/github/pdbreak/test.py(6)<module>()
            -> print 2
            (Pdb) l
            1       #!/usr/bin/env python
            2       # encoding: utf-8
            3
            4       print 1
            5       import pdbreak
            6  ->   print 2
            [EOF]
        
        
